sellerCard.oneLiner: Making a living through my passion, web development
sellerCard.description:
I'm a web developer with over 10 years of experience in building high-quality websites. I have extensive knowledge and I can work with various programming languages, CMS such as WordPress, and tools in the ways that benefit my clients the most. 
I will build secure, clean, and dynamic websites to fulfill your needs.
My flexibility, dedication, and problem-solving skills are my strong points.
I am looking for long-term and short-term projects.

description.content:
I'm a web developer with over 10 years of experience in building high-quality websites. I have built over a hundred websites for my clients over the years.

With this gig, I will build a full WordPress website from scratch for you.


WHAT IS INCLUDED:


  • WordPress Theme Installation and Setup
  • Plugins Installation and Setup
  • Responsive Design for All Devices
  • Converting Existing Website to Elementor
  • Converting PSD, Adobe XD, HTML to Elementor
  • Improve or Fix Existing Design
  • SEO Friendly
  • Performance Optimization / Fast Loading
  • Subscription & Payment Forms
  • Content Upload / Logo, Images, Text


HOW TO PROCEED:


  1. Contact me so we can discuss the details and I can be clear about what you want to achieve.
  2. We agree on a design and you send me your content so I can review it.
  3. If everything is good to go, I will send you a custom offer or tell you which gig better fits your needs.
  4. I will show you the completed WordPress website and get your feedback. Based on that I will do the final changes.


Please contact me before placing an order so we can discuss the project details. I will be happy to assist you and find a package that fits your needs better.


100% SATISFACTION GUARANTEED

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do we start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Please send me a message before placing an order. This way we can discuss the details and see which plan is most suitable for you. Every project is different so a conversation ahead of the order is highly recommended.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need from me?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will need all the content before I start working on the design and a couple websites or competitors to use as an example.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I don't have any content, can you write it for me?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
I am not a content writer so I would do a poor job at it. 
In order not to waste any time, I can fill the website with dummy content and you can replace it later when you have it ready.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Beside the content, I will need the Admin username and password to a self-hosted WordPress. If you don't have this ready at the time of the order, I will work the design on a local host and upload it to your server when it's finished.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I edit content by myself later or am I depended on you?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. WordPress and Elementor have made it easy for anyone to edit content without having any programming knowledge. I will even teach you the basics once the project is finished.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer website hosting or domain registration?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can host your website on a private virtual server, domain registration, and anything else required to have the server and website functional. Contact me for more information about this.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer support or maintenance after my website is launched?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I also offer custom maintenance packages to help keep your website running and up to date and secure with the latest web technology.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do I need to pay for Elementor Pro?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can get you started with Elementor Pro, but you will need to buy a license for it later on.

reviews.comment: The website Beso developed for my business has been a long time coming, and I couldnt be happier with the final result. The process wasnt without its challenges, but Besos patience and professionalism stood out every step of the way, even as unexpected changes caused delays. Not only is he a skilled developer, but he also excels in communicationhe took the time to explain and help me understand the web development process, even teaching me a few basics along the way. His extensive experience, impressive skill set, and willingness to share his knowledge made the entire experience seamless and enjoyable. If I need any more work done in the future, Beso will absolutely be my go-to guy. I highly recommend him to anyone looking for a talented, reliable, and communicative web developer.
